### ClickUp_AirbyteCustom · task — `custom_fields` keys

The `custom_fields` column is a JSON array. Keys currently extracted in SQL:

| Field Name | Type | Notes |
| --- | --- | --- |
| `Hubspot URL` | string | HubSpot company deep-link; `hubspot_company_id` parsed via regex `/0-2/(\d+)` |
| `Customer Type` | string (orderindex) | 0 = Flow+View, 1 = Flow, 2 = View, 3 = Sync |
| `Services` | JSON array | UUIDs mapped to Flow / View / Sync service options |
| `Total Facilities` | integer | Manual override of facility count |
| `Org Code` | JSON | Organization code |
| `🏠 Companies` | JSON array | Linked facility task objects — each contains `id`, `name`, `status` |
| `Billing Stop Date` | string (ms epoch) | Converted via `TIMESTAMP_MILLIS` |
| `Go-Live Date` | string (ms epoch) | Converted via `TIMESTAMP_MILLIS` |
| `Dev Onboarding Start Date` | string (ms epoch) | Converted via `TIMESTAMP_MILLIS` |

