## Appendix C — New Customer ID Propagation Workflow

This diagram illustrates the automated workflow that fires when a deal reaches **Closed Won** status in HubSpot. The workflow writes the `CovrID` back to ClickUp at the company, corporation, and contact levels via API, then propagates those identifiers downstream to Intercom and PostHog. The next daily Airbyte sync carries the updated values into BigQuery, ensuring the Customer Cube record is fully resolved within 24 hours.

